reviewText:
Can't explain my personal connection to this movie and I don't see hardly any movies more than once (except the Godfather, of course, and Barfly and well, just a handful) but this has stuck with me since it opened. I love Demi Moore. I love the buildup. I love the KID!!! Where is that KID since he made the movie?

Anyway, suspensful, well acted, with a great twist (at least for me.)

@BoweryBunny
